<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1037826" n="5v"/>
<lb/><note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895">Ad Franciscum Christ, Baslieam.</note>
<p><lb/>Ex <rs type="letter">literis</rs> Tuis, utut gratissimis imo plusquam dici potest gratis, non sine su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o dolore intellexi,
<lb/>quam male fecerim, quod me <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>veniri, sinistramque de me opinionem, quasi tui me ce<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>pisset oblivio, tibi obrepere passus fuerim. Fateor profecto et lubens agnosco, te justissimas ha<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>bere causas de tali conquerendi amico, qui secus ac promisit silere tamdiu quam officio
<lb/>amici defungi maluit, quique ut ea, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> jura ab ipso postulant, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stet <unclear reason="illegible">mone<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ri</unclear> opus habuit. Quoniam vero tu ipse <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> candore meo alienum esse putas, ut tui memoriam
<lb/>unquam deponam, ideo facile abs te silentii mei veniam me exoratum spero, etenim si
<lb/>tibi de integritate mea, ut persuasus sum, bene constat, ipse judicabis, nullam hic meam
<lb/>intercessisse culpam. Mirum hoc tibi forsan videbitur, quia tantum interea temporis
<lb/>effluxit, sed scias, <choice><orig><g ref="#ohat">ô</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> amice, quod diuturni hujus silentii nulla alia sit causa, quam
<lb/>perturbatus rerum mearum status, et irrequietus animus meus, qui mihi nequidem ad
    <lb/>proximos consanguineos vix ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-135542286">parentem</rs> <rs type="letter">literas</rs> dare permisit; inde enim ab adventu
<lb/>meo ad huc usque tempus ne per unicam horam mihi vere quieto aut l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>to esse licuit,
<lb/>quia cum <rs type="person">discipulo</rs> meo rem se longe aliter, quam putaveram, habere inveni. Statim
<lb/>certe ab initio in animo habui cum ipso <rs type="person">Patre</rs> meo <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basileam</rs> redire, et ob id jam ali<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>quot amicis valedixi, paulo post autem propositum mutavi hac spe fretus, rem in poste<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>rum melius, quam ab initio apparebat, successuram esse, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> spes, quia me fefellit, in
<lb/>causa est, cur primum illud propositum nihilominus exequi constituerim. Redibo
<lb/>igitur, si Deus voluerit, brevi <rs type="place">Basileam</rs>, et forte <rs type="person">discipulus</rs> mecum, dabiturque occa<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>sio amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vinculum arctius constringendi. Causas reditus mei, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> forsan 
<pb facs="1037827" n="6r"/> 
<lb/>non ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt, quas tibi imaginaris, tibi coram aperiam; unum tamen te celare non possum, quod au<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tem in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>nigmate tantum tibi propono, Comitis nempe <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-12388067X">Du Luc</rs> Gallici Ablegati <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1366601211">filium</rs> non mini<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>mam fuisse causam, quod res tam male successit. Sed h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c omnia tibi soli concredita sunto,
<lb/>nolo enim ut quisquam alius, quam fidissimus meus <rs type="person">amicus</rs> conditionis me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> gnarus sit.
<lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1132220874">Jer. Raillardi</rs> adventum maximo cum desiderio expecto, vereor autem <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>nisi statim profi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ciscatur<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> ut me in <rs type="place">Urbe</rs> inveniat, intra <date>octiduum</date> enim, ut credo, in <rs type="place">rus</rs> ibimus; si ta<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>men exacte mihi adventum ejus pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>nuntiare posses, venirem sane in <rs type="place">Urbem</rs> aut in vicum
<lb/><rs type="place" key="place_2660228">Jeggisdorf</rs>,<note type="comment">Jegenstorf</note> ubi necessario transiturus et forte pransurus est, distat enim hic vicus semi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>horio duntaxat ab <rs type="place" key="place_2660349">Hindelbanck</rs>, adeo ut ibi colloquendi et nos exhilarandi facilis si<unclear reason="illegible">t</unclear>
<lb/>occasio. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-135542286">Pater</rs> eum forsan <rs type="letter">epistola</rs> onerabit, quam, ut confido, mihi perferre non dedigna<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>bitur; prosperum ipsi iter apprecari et plurimam salutem meo nomine nuntiare non recu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>sabis. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-123503094">Nic. Schwartzium</rs> disputasse et post <date>Pascha</date> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661552">Bernam</rs> venturum esse jam cognovi,
<lb/>sed confide, non ambo te derelinquent <rs type="person">Nicolai</rs><!-- Zwei Nicolas: gemeint sind Nic. I B.s Vater und Nic. Schwarz -->. Saluta eum, et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1072469103">Beckium</rs>, quem studia Ju<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ri<unclear>s</unclear> nunc iterum tractare l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus audio, saluta omnes <rs type="person">amicos</rs>, <rs type="person">Thurnisios</rs> cumprimis et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-122123158">Grun<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>dlerum</rs>, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quo unum <rs type="biblio">Disputationis</rs>, si modo impressa fuerit, exemplar pete, mihique
<lb/>illud per <rs type="person">Raillardum</rs> mitte. Denique si <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-141546573">D. Battierio</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1366600037 pers_DE-588-1366599853">Parentibus</rs> item tuis hono<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ratissimis officiosissimam nuntiabis salutem, nihil facies quod non sit gratissimum.</p>
<closer><salute>Tu autem Vale quam optime et in amore persevera.</salute> <dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661552">Bern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1710-03-12">12. Martii 1710</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
